dod-te-guidebook pack — content licence
========================================

This pack is derived from:
    Test and Evaluation Enterprise Guidebook
    US Department of Defense, Office of the Under Secretary of Defense for
    Research and Engineering (OUSD R&E), August 2022

Source licence: Public Domain (US Government work, 17 U.S.C. 105); Distribution
