No licence conditions are carried forward into this pack: there is no attribution,
non-commercial, or share-alike obligation, because the source carries none.
Attribution to the US Department of Defense (OUSD R&E) is provided as a courtesy
(see the repository NOTICE), not a legal obligation. The DoD does not endorse this
pack or its authors.

This pack reproduces no long verbatim passages of the source; its content is
synthesized, transformed reference notes (verified mechanically by
tools/check_overlap.py). The source guidebook is GUIDANCE, not policy — the binding
test-and-evaluation requirements live in DoDI 5000.89 and the related DoDI
5000-series issuances and Title 10 statutes (e.g., 10 U.S.C. §§ 4171, 4172).

